    <tags>dot-agent dotfiles ai-agent claude cursor git backup config sync</tags>
    <summary>Sync AI coding assistant configuration across machines using git</summary>
    <description>
Sync AI coding assistant configuration across machines using git.
Supports Claude Code, Cursor, Hermes Agent, OpenAI Codex, Gemini CLI, GitHub Copilot CLI, and Antigravity CLI on macOS, Linux, and Windows.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/cthulhu/dot-agent/releases</releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="tools\**" target="tools" />
  </files>
